  Locus:
    Page: 493
    Verse: 12
Tags:
  - Wisdom
---
If we desire wisdom we must seek for it, work for it, and pray for it. We
must patiently strive for the wisdom that we desire and then we must pass
it out to others who are also seeking wisdom.
